  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`IComposeSessionService` + `ComposeSessionService` compile; no AI client injected; no new session entity introduced.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`RebindToDocumentIdAsync` is idempotent — second call with the same new id is a no-op.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`EnsureSessionForDocumentAsync` returns a session bound via existing ChatSessionManager (no new Redis key shape or Cosmos partition).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF builds clean; publish-size delta ≤+0.5 MB; no new HIGH CVE.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">TASK-INDEX.md status for task 023 is ✅.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

