  <notes>
    <completion date="2026-06-29" rigor="FULL">
      <summary>
        ComposeSessionService implemented as a thin binding seam over the existing
        ChatSessionManager three-tier persistence pipeline (Redis hot → Cosmos warm
        → Dataverse cold). Zero new session entity, zero new Redis keys, zero new
        Cosmos partitions, zero new Dataverse columns — pure delegation + two
        idempotency short-circuits on RebindToDocumentIdAsync (caller-asserted
        equality + stored-already-at-target). Out-of-order Save races logged at
        Warning with new-value-wins semantics.
      </summary>
      <files-created>
        <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Compose/IComposeSessionService.cs</file>
        <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Compose/ComposeSessionService.cs</file>
        <file>tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Compose/ComposeSessionServiceTests.cs (9 tests, all passing)</file>
      </files-created>
      <chat-session-reuse>
        <consumed>Sprk.Bff.Api.Services.Ai.Chat.ChatSessionManager (Scoped; unconditional per AnalysisServicesModule.cs:275 line B4)</consumed>
        <reused-methods>CreateSessionAsync, GetSessionAsync, UpdateSessionCacheAsync (internal)</reused-methods>
        <model>Sprk.Bff.Api.Models.Ai.Chat.ChatSession (immutable record; record `with` expression mirrors ChatHistoryManager.AddMessageAsync pattern)</model>
        <persistence-tiers>Redis (tenant:{tenantId}:session:{sessionId}:v1 — FR-05) + Cosmos write-through (fire-and-forget, D-06) + Dataverse sprk_aichatsummary (cold audit) — all unchanged.</persistence-tiers>
      </chat-session-reuse>
      <documentid-binding>
        <path-b>DocumentId = SPE drive-item id (ephemeral); HostContext=null (not extended in R1).</path-b>
        <path-a>DocumentId = sprk_documentid (post-promotion); RebindToDocumentIdAsync idempotent on (1) currentDocumentId==newDocumentId, (2) session.DocumentId==newDocumentId.</path-a>
        <out-of-order-race>caller-asserted current ≠ stored current → log Warning + proceed (new-value-wins).</out-of-order-race>
      </documentid-binding>
